&lt;p data-start=&quot;309&quot; data-end=&quot;671&quot;&gt;Are you a skilled HVAC Warranty technician with a talent for troubleshooting and a commitment to doing the job right the first time?&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;433&quot; data-end=&quot;454&quot;&gt;ProSkill Services&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking an experienced &lt;strong data-start=&quot;481&quot; data-end=&quot;516&quot;&gt;HVAC Warranty Repair Technician&lt;/strong&gt; to join our trusted team. If you excel at refrigerant-related repairs and take pride in delivering exceptional customer service, we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;703&quot; data-end=&quot;868&quot;&gt;As a Warranty Repair Technician, you’ll be a critical part of maintaining ProSkill’s reputation for fast, reliable, and high-quality service. In this role, you will&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform &lt;strong&gt;warranty repairs&lt;/strong&gt;, troubleshooting, and system maintenance under manufacturer/service contract terms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct diagnostics, estimate repair needs, and execute fixes efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete documentation, maintain truck stock, and ensure safety/compliance on every job.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide top-notch customer service, representing ProSkill’s trusted reputation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1437&quot; data-end=&quot;1460&quot;&gt;Qualifications and Requirements:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1464&quot; data-end=&quot;1555&quot;&gt;3–5+ years of HVAC service experience, preferably in residential repair and warranty work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1558&quot; data-end=&quot;1682&quot;&gt;Strong diagnostic skills and experience with a range of residential HVAC systems (heat pumps, furnaces, mini-splits, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1685&quot; data-end=&quot;1761&quot;&gt;Valid EPA certification and applicable HVAC trade license (where required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1764&quot; data-end=&quot;1844&quot;&gt;Clean driving record and ability to pass a background check and drug screening&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1847&quot; data-end=&quot;1934&quot;&gt;Ability to work independently in variable conditions (attics, crawl spaces, rooftops)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1937&quot; data-end=&quot;2006&quot;&gt;Strong customer communication skills and a solutions-driven mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
